condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Annual Report: FA reference Section III.A, Schedule 2 | Description :Preparation of annual project progressreports | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Appointment of Auditor: FA reference Section III.B.4 | Description :The Recipient shall, not later than sixmonths after the Effective Date, appoint the independent auditors in accordance with the provisions of Section IV of this Schedule,with qualifications, experience and terms of reference satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :20-Feb-2014

Finance Agreement :Base line Surveys : FA reference Section II.E.6b | Description :The FMOH shall engage, not later than June 30,2012, the NBS to carry out household surveys and the NPoPC to carry out health facility surveys to collect health data relevant forthe purposes of the Project, under terms of reference and in a manner acceptable to the Association. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :DLI: FA reference Schedules 4, 5 and 6 | Description :Matrices with Disbursement Linked Indicators for Statesand LGAs, with corresponding allocations of amounts per each State/LGA and per DLI | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Disbursement: FA reference Section V, Schedule 2 | Description :Withdrawal schedule with categories ofexpenditures and related disbursement conditions: Conditions for disbursement of DLI payments to States and LGAs: execution ofindividual grant agreements and meeting of DLIs by each respective State and LGA; Withdrawal schedule with categories ofexpenditures and related disbursement conditions | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Effectiveness: FA reference Sections 4.01 & 4.03 | Description :At least one subsidiary agreement with aparticipating State executed; provision for cross-effectiveness of IDA Financing Agreement and HRITF Grant Agreement; and adoptionof satisfactory Project Implementation Manual | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :FM/ Audit Arrangement: FA reference Section III.B, Schedule 2 | Description :Standard financial managementcovenants, including obligation to submit interim financial reports and annual project audits, as well as an additional requirementfor submission of annual audits of health sector expenditures | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Health Care Waste Management Plan: FA reference Section II.C, Schedule 2 | Description :Obligation to implementthe project in accordance with the Health Care Waste Management Plan | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Institutional Arrangement: Financing Agreement reference Section I, Schedule 2 | Description :Provisionsrequiring the maintenance of relevant Project management structures at federal, state. LGA and facility level, i.e. federal andstate steering committees and working groups, FMOH, NPHCDA, SMOH, SPHCDAs, LGAs, LGA RBF steering committees, and health facilityRBF committees | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LGA PHC and DLI payment: FA reference Section II.E, Schedule 2 | Description :Terms and conditions fordetermining, verifying and providing payments to health facilities and LGA PHC departments, and DLI payments to LGAs | Frequency:Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Procurement Arrangement: FA reference Section IV, Schedule 2 | Description :Standard provisions on procurementmethods and procedures | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Manual : FA reference Section II.A, Schedule 2 | Description :Obligation to carry out theproject in accordance with a project implementation manual satisfactory to the Bank | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :RBF Technical Assistance : FA reference Section II.E.6a | Description :The NPHCDA shall engage, not later thanOctober 31, 2012, an independent expert whose terms of reference, qualifications and experience shall be satisfactory to theAssociation, to conduct ex-post verifications of the delivery of the Packages of Health Services by each Participating HealthFacility. | Due Date :31-Oct-2012

Finance Agreement :Retroactive financing: FA reference: Section V.B.1a | Description :No withdrawal shall be made for payments madeprior to the date of this Agreement, except that withdrawals up to an aggregate amount not to exceed $3,600,000 equivalent may bemade for payments made to Participating States and Participating LGAs prior to this date but on or after November 15, 2011, forState EEPs and LGA EEPs under Category 2 | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Retroactive financing: GA reference , Section V.B.1a | Description :No withdrawal shall be made for paymentsmade prior to the date of this Agreement, except that withdrawals up to an aggregate amount not to exceed $500,000 equivalent maybe made for payments made to Participating States and Participating LGAs prior to this date but on or after November 15, 2011, forState EEPs and LGA EEPs under Category 2 | Due Date :22-Aug-2013

Finance Agreement :Subsidiary Agreement: FA reference Section II.D & Section V.B.1, Schedule 2 | Description :Obligation to executesubsidiary agreements between the Borrower and the participating States, and terms and conditions for determining, verifying andproviding DLI payments to the States | Frequency :Yearly
